[02:00.32]Such well-meaning people just don't understand.
[02:05.22]Scientists must communicate their message to the public in a compassionate,
[02:10.75]understandable way¡ªin human terms,
[02:15.04]not in the language of molecular biology.
[02:18.08]We need to make clear the connection between animal research
[02:23.37]and a grandmother's hip replacement,
[02:26.38]a father's bypass operation,
[02:29.04]a baby's vaccinations, and even a pet's shots.
[02:33.50]To those who are unaware that animal research
[02:36.65]was needed to produce these treatments,
[02:39.19]as well as new treatments and vaccines,
